<tr>
  <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-bottom: 15px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; color: #1a1a2e; margin: 0 0 10px;">Your subscription has been canceled</h2>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-bottom: 10px;">
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 15px;">
      Hi {{ admin.name | default: "there" }},
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 15px;">
      Your AirysChat subscription for <strong>{{ account.name }}</strong> has been canceled.
      Your account has been downgraded to the Free plan.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 15px;">
      Your data is still safe and accessible. However, features above the Free plan limits
      (additional agents, inboxes, and AI tokens) are no longer available.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 15px;">
      You can resubscribe at any time to regain full access.
    </p>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="vertical-align: top; padding: 15px 0;">
    <a href="{{ billing_url }}"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #0080f8; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
      Resubscribe
    </a>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-top: 15px;">
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;">
      If you have any feedback about why you canceled, we'd love to hear from you — just reply to this email.
    </p>
  </td>
</tr>
